## Available Skills

When the task matches, invoke these skills:
- `/daily-review` — orchestrate full daily review
- `/weekly-review` — Saturday review + planning
- `/process-inbox` — Telegram + Notion inbox processing
- `/scrum` — check status of all dispatched agents
- `/suggest-tasks` — scan projects and propose prioritized tasks
- `/dispatch-approved` — dispatch approved tasks

